Action Input: {"reservation_type": "flight", "query": "future flight", "max_results": 5}
Observation: {"reservations": []} 

Thought: There are still no future flight reservations found. Since I cannot find any flights, I will prepare an email to inform Amy Watson that there are no flights available for Ada Lovelace. 
